-------------Client-----------------
Type in the following command to install

curl http://marcopolo.github.com/wootLights/installWootmit.sh | sh






-------------Server-----------------

The server with the woot lights must be running this
use dnotify -M ./ -e sh onChange.sh 
to make it work


make sure to 
chmod a+x onChange.sh
chmod a+x turnMeOn.py
